<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Your OTP Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333333;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .otp-box {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      background: #f0f4ff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: #2a47ec;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
    }
    p {
      color: #555555;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      margin-top: 25px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>
    <p>
      You recently requested to reset your password. Use the OTP below to complete your request.
    </p>

    <div class="otp-box">
      {{otp}}
    </div>

    <p>
      This OTP is valid for <strong>{{expiry}}</strong>. Please do not share this code with anyone.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you didnâ€™t request this, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{year}} Dating App. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
